    <item>
      <title>Version 0.15</title>
      <sparkle:version>6</sparkle:version>
      <sparkle:shortVersionString>0.15</sparkle:shortVersionString>
      <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>26.4</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
      <pubDate>Sat, 30 May 2026 21:53:34 +0000</pubDate>
      <description><![CDATA[
        <h2>What's New in 0.15</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Non-destructive annotations. Edits are no longer flattened permanently — screenshots keep their original pixels and a re-editable .screendrop sidecar, so you can reopen and tweak annotations any time after saving.</li>
          <li>Smarter clipboard &amp; saving. After editing, the latest version is automatically re-copied to the clipboard and the existing saved file is overwritten in place — no more stale copies or duplicate files.</li>
          <li>Cloud setup is much smoother. A secure upload token is generated for you (with Copy / Reveal / Regenerate), and Verify Connection now provisions your worker's database automatically — no manual migration step after a one-click deploy.</li>
          <li>Worker update notifications. The app detects when your deployed Cloud worker is behind and shows a non-blocking "update available" notice with a how-to link.</li>
          <li>Cloud settings redesign. Cleaner, less cluttered layout with native input fields, an inline token reveal, and a collapsible setup guide.</li>
        </ul>
      ]]></description>
