        <ul>
          <li>Capture fullscreen, window, or custom area screenshots with global hotkeys (Option+1/2/3)</li>
          <li>Annotate screenshots with rectangles, ellipses, arrows, freehand drawing, text, numbered circles, and pixelate/blur tools</li>
